CLEARING THE LOGS
shred -fzvu /var/log/auth.log
--logs are stored in the /var/log dir
--shred permanently deletes the the logs permenently by re writing the data multiple times with 1s and 0s
--this erases the traces of the data to th absolute peak

CLEARING THE BASH HISTORY FILE
>.bash_history
--null redirect
--this clears the file
-- for every user theres a bash_history file
